  "body": "Currently, the wallet instance is only unset when leaving the `Account View & Send` tab.\r\n\r\n- [ ] Clear wallet state when a user exists the following routes: \r\n1. Sign and Verify (depending on in if they signed in to sign a message, or only verified)\r\n2. Contracts (depending on if they signed in to broadcast a contract)\r\n3. Swap (depending on if they hit stage 3 and activated lite send. \r\n\r\n\r\nFuture:\r\n- [ ] Clear state when exiting ENS. ",
