    "body": "Probably the easiest way to do this would just be to have one componentWillUnmount on TabSection component, or to have something watch path changes and remove the instance if the base path changes (i.e. /account/send to /account/info won't remove it, but /account/send to /sign-and-verify would.)\r\n\r\nLikewise, we could also move the logout notification to tab section, just \"render\" it (so that it'll show on navigation) when they have a wallet in redux.",
